# Local secrets / per-environment overrides.
# No whitelist exception — .env.*.example files have historically
# shipped real URLs/secrets by mistake (see commit b53f99f). If you
# need a template, put a fake-values block in the service README
# instead of a dotfile git will track.
.env
.env.*
.run/
